text:
Oh, Producer-san...
Sorry, I'm feeling a bit sleepy...

I ended up staying up late,
chatting with everyone.

I guess when you think it's the end,
it gets a bit lonely...

I see. The end of time spent together
always feels a bit regretful, doesn't it?

But, maybe it's not really the end since we're in the
same agency, there will be chances to hang out together.

Yeah, for now,
make sure to get some rest on your way home.
